"Is that wand still turned on?" said Sligh.\par
"Jeff, ask me a question I can lie to."\par
"Are you interested in women, Fargo?"\par
"Not at all," said Fargo, who then let out a wild cry and dropped the wand. "Did you have to ask me for that \i big \i0 a lie?" he said, holding both sides. His eyes were watering.\par
